foreignObject.p: Overview tree for samples collected in USA, California, San Joaquin County between 2022-08-09 and 2022-11-01
Showing 476 of 1175 genomes sampled between Aug 2021 and Oct 2022.

The data presented here is intended to rapidly disseminate analysis of important pathogens. Unpublished data is included with permission of the data generators, and does not impact their right to publish. A full list of sequence authors is available via nextstrain.org.

p.a: Hadfield et al, Nextstrain: real-time tracking of pathogen evolution, Bioinformatics (2018)
Sagulenko et al, TreeTime: Maximum-likelihood phylodynamic analysis, Virus Evolution (2017)
